msgctxt "1||gun0||information"
msgid "A gun designed for beginning fishermen. It has\r\nlow power, but great aim and spear count."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2||gun1||information"
msgid "A powerful weapon perfect for tackling bosses.\r\nHowever, low spear capacity hinders it in normal use."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3||gun2||information"
msgid "This speargun can load a lot of low damage shots,\r\nso you need to make every shot count."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4||gun3||information"
msgid "A modified version of the Standard Speargun.\r\nIts high performance doesn't drag down usability."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||gun4||information"
msgid "Extremely high damage, but can only load a few\r\nspears at a time. Make sure you don't miss."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||gun5||information"
msgid "The denizens of the sea will cower before the\r\nhigh damage and spear count of this elite weapon."
msgstr ""

